Rumah pasti berantakan. Bagaimana ini?

713
00:56:54,443 --> 00:56:57,071
Sudah kubilang, berbenah jika sempat.

714
00:56:58,655 --> 00:57:01,116
Kukira punggungku akan patah kemarin.

715
00:57:01,742 --> 00:57:03,660
Kerja bagus, Nak.

716
00:57:04,078 --> 00:57:05,079
Duduklah.

717
00:57:11,126 --> 00:57:14,129
Saat aku kecil, rumah ini terlihat besar.

718
00:57:18,092 --> 00:57:20,010
- Ibu.
- Ya?

719
00:57:21,261 --> 00:57:23,388
Kenapa tak pernah membicarakan Kakak?

720
00:57:27,226 --> 00:57:28,727
Jika dipikirkan,

721
00:57:30,771 --> 00:57:32,314
setelah kejadian itu,

722
00:57:33,190 --> 00:57:34,775
Ibu tak pernah membicarakan dia.

723
00:57:35,567 --> 00:57:37,027
Tak pernah membahas.

724
00:57:37,986 --> 00:57:40,864
Kau pun baru kali ini membicarakan dia.

725
00:57:42,950 --> 00:57:44,076
Benar.

726
00:57:45,536 --> 00:57:47,246
Astaga, lama sekali.

727
00:57:50,374 --> 00:57:51,500
Ibu bagaimana?

728
00:57:52,417 --> 00:57:53,544
Masih sering

729
00:57:54,461 --> 00:57:55,671
memikirkan Kakak?

730
00:57:58,549 --> 00:58:00,384
Kadang kala.

731
00:58:03,262 --> 00:58:06,890
Adakalanya, entah karena apa,

732
00:58:08,350 --> 00:58:10,519
aku terbangun di tengah malam

733
00:58:10,978 --> 00:58:12,771
dan menangis.

734
00:58:13,897 --> 00:58:15,357
Di hari lain,

735
00:58:16,775 --> 00:58:21,196
aku kaget karena sama sekali
tak memikirkannya,

736
00:58:21,530 --> 00:58:22,823
bahkan satu kali pun.

737
00:58:24,700 --> 00:58:26,785
Setelah sekian lama, beginilah.

738
00:58:29,663 --> 00:58:30,706
Hari-hariku

739
00:58:31,039 --> 00:58:33,458
tak selalu terasa menyakitkan.

740
00:58:35,210 --> 00:58:38,422
Hari-hariku tak selalu dipenuhi
pikiran tentangnya.

741
00:58:40,215 --> 00:58:42,342
Datang dan pergi. Batasnya jadi samar.

742
00:58:44,094 --> 00:58:45,429
Begitulah kehidupan.

743
00:58:50,434 --> 00:58:52,227
Kau pun pasti terbebani.

744
00:58:56,190 --> 00:58:58,859
Tidak. Aku tak apa karena ada Ibu.

745
00:58:59,860 --> 00:59:01,987
Aku pun bisa bertahan berkatmu.

746
00:59:17,252 --> 00:59:19,129
<i>Jo Tae-sik.</i>

747
00:59:19,880 --> 00:59:21,381
Tae-sik!

748
00:59:24,384 --> 00:59:25,219
Hei, Tae-sik.

749
00:59:26,011 --> 00:59:27,888
Sudah kubilang, tunggu.

750
00:59:32,142 --> 00:59:34,102
Ayo pergi bersama.

751
00:59:42,945 --> 00:59:44,863
Sejak kapan kau jadi tinggi?

752
00:59:46,156 --> 00:59:47,866
Kau masih kurus.

753
00:59:48,575 --> 00:59:49,701
Makan tak teratur?

754
00:59:49,826 --> 00:59:50,911
Apa maksudmu?

755
00:59:50,994 --> 00:59:53,830
Aku makan banyak, juga jadi gemuk.

756
00:59:55,249 --> 00:59:57,125
Kini, aku polisi.

757
00:59:58,210 --> 00:59:59,920
Aku tahu.

758
01:00:04,258 --> 01:00:05,551
Tak apa, Tae-sik.

759
01:00:07,886 --> 01:00:09,763
Dengar kata Ibu tadi, bukan?

760
01:00:10,681 --> 01:00:12,182
Begitulah kehidupan.

761
01:00:12,266 --> 01:00:14,393
Ada hari baik dan hari buruk.

762
01:00:17,396 --> 01:00:20,232
Aku tahu kau menyiksa diri
karena kejadian yang menimpaku.

763
01:00:20,440 --> 01:00:22,359
Berhentilah memikirkanku.

764
01:00:30,284 --> 01:00:32,744
Ga-yeon, di mana kau?

765
01:00:35,163 --> 01:00:36,456
Ga-yeon.

766
01:00:37,291 --> 01:00:40,335
- Ga-yeon.
- Astaga, dasar cengeng.

767
01:00:40,419 --> 01:00:42,504
Ga-yeon, kau di mana?

768
01:00:42,588 --> 01:00:44,506
Berhenti mengerjaiku.

769
01:00:44,923 --> 01:00:46,174
Ga-yeon.

770
01:00:46,466 --> 01:00:48,844
- Berbahagialah, Dik.
- Kau di mana, Ga-yeon?

771
01:01:22,044 --> 01:01:24,129
Terimalah ini!

772
01:01:25,797 --> 01:01:27,758
Ayo!

773
01:01:28,467 --> 01:01:30,344
Serbu!

774
01:01:57,496 --> 01:01:58,789
Eun-seong.

775
01:02:02,668 --> 01:02:05,045
Ini kali pertama kupanggil nama aslimu.

776
01:02:13,428 --> 01:02:14,680
Eun-seong.

777
01:02:18,600 --> 01:02:20,102
Yu Eun-seong.

778
01:02:38,120 --> 01:02:39,037
<i>Maafkan aku</i>

779
01:02:40,789 --> 01:02:42,624
<i>karena kita tak bisa bersama lebih lama.</i>

